div.span: When a bug is reported during the release cycle, QA opens a bug which completes with a developer uploading a new package to focal-dev with a version that contains a patch component so that it sorts greater than the version being QA'd but less than the next version that has new features and go through a future release cycle. QA then fast tracks that bug fix up through to the place where the bug was reported.
